OL,3,CElderly woman's body found two miles
OL,4,Cfrom crash site
OL,6,FThe body of an elderly woman who was
OL,7,Fhit by a lorry was found more than two
OL,8,Fmiles from the site of the crash in
OL,9,FBradford.
OL,11,FThe 77-year-old was involved in a
OL,12,Fcollision on Harrogate Road, near its
OL,13,Fjunction with Killinghall Road, at
OL,14,Fabout 5.20pm on Wednesday, 15 April.
OL,16,FWest Yorkshire Police said her body
OL,17,Fwas then found on Neville Road,
OL,18,Fseveral minutes' drive away. She died
OL,19,Fat the scene.
