CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1776618353
OL,3,CElderly woman's body found two miles
OL,4,Cfrom crash site
OL,6,FIt is believed she had been carried by
OL,7,Fthe lorry until it came to a stop.
OL,9,FA 55-year-old man was arrested on
OL,10,Fsuspicion of causing death by
OL,11,Fdangerous driving. He has since been
OL,12,Fbailed pending further enquiries.
OL,14,FDet Insp Paul Conroy, of the Major
OL,15,FCollision Enquiry Team, said: "This is
OL,16,Fan extremely upsetting incident
OL,17,Finvolving an elderly pedestrian in
OL,18,FBradford. Our thoughts go out to the
OL,19,Ffamily who are being supported by
OL,20,Fspecially trained officers.
OL,26,@wD@_OU
